        <p>Learn how medical device claims can overlap with broader product liability litigation.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="consumer-product-case-review.html" class="card">
        <h3>Start a Medical Device Case Review</h3>
        <p>Submit basic information about a medical device injury for review.</p>
      </a>
      <a href="https://lawsuitinformer.com/medical-device-lawsuits.html" class="card">
        <h3>Medical Device Lawsuit Guide</h3>
        <p>Read Lawsuit Informer’s background guide on medical device litigation and claim evaluation.</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<section class="final">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Considering a medical device case review?</h2>
    <p>
      If you believe a medical device may be connected to a serious injury, complication,
      revision surgery, infection, device failure, or other harm, you can explore whether case review fits.
    </p>
    <div class="final__ctas">
      <a href="case-review.html" class="btn btn--dark btn--lg">Start Free Case Review</a>
      <a href="how-case-review-works.html" class="btn btn--outline btn--lg">How Case Review Works</a>
    </div>
    <p class="small-text" style="margin-top: 22px;">
      A case review request does not guarantee eligibility, compensation, contact from a law firm, or legal representation.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

